title: Memphis upsets No. 13 Ole Miss 37-24

(AP Photo/Mark Humphrey) Posted: Saturday, October 17, 2015 3:44 pm Memphis upsets No. 13 Ole Miss 37-24 Associated Press | 0 comments 
MEMPHIS, Tenn. (AP) — Paxton Lynch threw for 384 yards and three touchdowns as Memphis stunned No. 13 Mississippi 37-24 on Saturday. 
Memphis (6-0) has won 13 straight games dating back to last season, which is the third longest streak in the nation.
